fields.name: AllocatedOutboundPorts
fields.description: The desired number of allocated SNAT ports per VM. Allowed values are in the range of 0 to 64000 (inclusive). The default value is 0 which results in Azure dynamically allocating ports.

fields.name: BackendPoolType
fields.description: The type of the managed inbound Load Balancer BackendPool.

fields.name: EffectiveOutboundIPs
fields.description: The effective outbound IP resources of the cluster load balancer.

fields.name: EnableMultipleStandardLoadBalancers
fields.description: Enable multiple standard load balancers per AKS cluster or not.

fields.name: IdleTimeoutInMinutes
fields.description: Desired outbound flow idle timeout in minutes. Allowed values are in the range of 4 to 120 (inclusive). The default value is 30 minutes.

fields.name: ManagedOutboundIPs
fields.description: Desired managed outbound IPs for the cluster load balancer.

fields.name: OutboundIPPrefixes
fields.description: Desired outbound IP Prefix resources for the cluster load balancer.

fields.name: OutboundIPs
fields.description: Desired outbound IP resources for the cluster load balancer.
